{"questionId":"21923","questionHtml":"<p>Write down the conclusion to the test. Give a reason for your answer.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><msup><mi>χ</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>calc</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>54</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>8</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>54347</mn><mo>…</mo></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; <strong>OR</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi></math>-value&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>0736</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>0735802</mn><mo>…</mo><mo>)</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo></math> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A2</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>8</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>54</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>49</mn></math>&nbsp; <strong>OR</strong>&nbsp; <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>0736</mn><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>05</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong><em>R1</em></strong></p>\n<p>therefore there is insufficient evidence to reject <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>0</mn></msub></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>(i.e. the data satisfies the model)</p>\n<p><br><strong>Note:</strong> Do not award <em><strong>R0A1</strong></em>. Accept “accept” or “do not reject” in place of “insufficient evidence to reject”. <br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Award the <em><strong>R1</strong></em> for comparing their <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi></math>-value with <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>05</mn></math> or their <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>χ</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math> value with <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>9</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>49</mn></math> and then <em><strong>FT</strong></em> their final conclusion.</p>\n<p><em><strong><br>[4 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"21923","referenceCode":"21M.1.SL.TZ2.11b.ii","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Write down the conclusion to the test. Give a reason for your answer.","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"b.ii","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 4]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 4—Statistics and probability","Topic 4—Statistics and probability","SL 4.11—Expected, observed, hypotheses, chi squared, gof, t-test"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}